article.description: — Shykeim Phillips had 16 points and six rebounds as UNC Wilmington topped Delaware 69-62 on Saturday.
article.headline: Phillips lifts UNC Wilmington over Delaware 69-62
article.linkText: Phillips lifts UNC Wilmington over Delaware 69-62
article.story: NEWARK, Del. -- — Shykeim Phillips had 16 points and six rebounds as UNC Wilmington topped Delaware 69-62 on Saturday. Amari Kelly had 14 points and seven rebounds for UNC Wilmington (21-8, 15-3 Colonial Athletic Association). James Baker Jr. and Jaylen Sims added 12 points apiece. Delaware totaled 23 points in the first half, a season low for the team. Jyare Davis scored a career-high 23 points and had seven rebounds for the Fightin' Blue Hens (19-11, 10-7). Jameer Nelson Jr. added 12 points and six rebounds. Andrew Carr had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
